item.title: The Student's Guide To Becoming A Successful Startup Founder
item.description: If you're a high school or college student with big dreams of starting your own company, this video is for you. Dalton Caldwell and Michael Seibel, two startup founders who started in the early 20s and are now top investors, sit down to share the hard-won advice they wish they had known back in high school... Feed: http://backtracks.fm/ycombinator/ycombinator/feed
